      <p class="hero-eyebrow" data-reveal>Polars Daily Log</p>
      <h1 class="hero-title" data-reveal>
        每天都干了啥，<br />
        不用你自己回忆。
      </h1>
      <p class="hero-sub" data-reveal>
        一个 AI-native 的个人工作活动聚合器。自动抓你每台机器的前台活动和 Git commits，
        LLM 合并成每日工作日志，一键推到 Jira。所有数据只在你自己的机器上。
      </p>
      <div class="hero-cta" data-reveal>
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="#install">
          立即开始
        </a>
        <a class="btn btn-text" href={repoUrl} target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          GitHub 源码 <span class="arrow" aria-hidden="true">↗</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- INSTALL ──────────────────────────────────────────────── -->
    <section class="install" id="install">
      <div class="section-inner">
        <div class="install-head" data-reveal>
          <p class="eyebrow">安装</p>
          <h2 class="section-title">
            一行命令，<br class="br-narrow" />
            在你自己机器上跑起来。
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="install-grid">
          <div class="install-card" data-reveal>
            <div class="install-card-head">
              <span class="install-label">最常见</span>
              <h3>一体机：Server + Collector</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="install-code">
              <div class="install-code-bar">
                <span>安装命令</span>
                <button
                  class="install-copy-btn"
                  type="button"
                  data-copy-button
                  data-copy="curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Conner2077/polars-daily-log/master/bootstrap.sh | bash"
                >
                  复制
                </button>
              </div>
              <pre><code>curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Conner2077/polars-daily-log/master/bootstrap.sh | bash</code></pre>
            </div>
            <p>自动下载最新 release、解压、执行 <code>install.sh</code>。装完访问 <code>http://127.0.0.1:8888</code>。</p>
          </div>
          <div class="install-card" data-reveal style="--delay: 100ms;">
            <div class="install-card-head">
              <span class="install-label">多机汇总</span>
              <h3>其他设备只装 Collector</h3>
            </div>
            <div class="install-code">
              <div class="install-code-bar">
                <span>安装命令</span>
                <button
                  class="install-copy-btn"
                  type="button"
                  data-copy-button
                  data-copy={"curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Conner2077/polars-daily-log/master/bootstrap.sh \\\n  | PDL_ROLE=collector \\\n    PDL_SERVER_URL=http://你的hub:8888 \\\n    PDL_COLLECTOR_NAME=macbook \\\n    bash"}
                >
                  复制
                </button>
              </div>
              <pre><code>{`curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Conner2077/polars-daily-log/master/bootstrap.sh \\
  | PDL_ROLE=collector \\
    PDL_SERVER_URL=http://你的hub:8888 \\
    PDL_COLLECTOR_NAME=macbook \\
    bash`}</code></pre>
            </div>
            <p>环境变量非交互装，适合把自己的 MacBook / Linux / 台式机批量推给 hub。</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <p class="install-foot">
          Windows 用户请跑 <code>install.ps1</code>（实验性）— 详见
          <a href={`${repoUrl}#readme`} target="_blank" rel="noopener">README</a>。
        </p>
      </div>
